Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默地为你着想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是悄悄藏在你看不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以平时毫无察觉地生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一旦回过神来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你着想的那个人的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会朦胧地浮现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果激烈地浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们就称之为…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 我今天做了烤奶油马铃薯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想让爸爸妈妈吃到好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坑坑洼洼的 样子糟糕得不好意思拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 一点也不会糟糕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为里面充满了小爱的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为蓝华今天去参加公司员工的旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有我跟爱丽丝两个人一起练习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的声音好好听 好好听哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为领航员最重要的是划船的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 难道你心情不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让比你年长的我来听你倾诉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事都不要客气 告诉姐姐吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…我的左手太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近发觉我的左手非常笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟右手比 既无法拿好筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法写出端正的字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那个…有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我正在惩罚左手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太依赖右手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都把所有事情交给右手做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把这当作理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有想办法解决过这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近养了一只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:20.04,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 想要守护的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是领航员协会中最顶尖的橙色行星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是宿舍严禁养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗？爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手特训？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它嘛嘛地叫 就取名为小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前它被丢弃在路边时 被我捡回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一个很寂寞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才找我商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想找蓝华前辈商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不巧她去公司员工的旅行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才找了灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带回我们公司里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给亚利亚社长圆不隆咚的肚子造成大危机的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛 别叫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不是奇怪的人…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是跟我同寝室的雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你说进房间前要敲门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才被你吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你了 我是亚利亚公司的水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一位是我们公司的亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？爱丽丝 雅典娜前辈是不是长得跟刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一位唱着美妙歌声的人有一点像？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就是她本人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三大精灵之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就属雅典娜前辈的Canzone最为有名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}Canzone：意大利语「歌」的意思 这里特指船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人就是传说中的雅典娜前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈要住下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前请先换上本公司的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那样超级显眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 小嘛会不会被雅典娜前辈发现呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止都还能应付过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为雅典娜前辈超级喜欢发呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…好像豪华餐厅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一日三餐大都是在这里解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 这杯水是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没发觉是雅典娜前辈帮她拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈又把全部的奶精放下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看雅典娜前辈那样 她可是个很笨拙的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常在走廊上跌倒 还经常把饮料打翻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是连最重要的事情都会忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话的时候还会自己不小心把电话挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说她有多笨拙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概跟我的左手差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 不可以这样说自己的前辈啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们两个都完全不在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚会跟亚利亚社长在您宿舍暂住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爱找麻烦 这时候就要用左手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 请您先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛 吃饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小嘛的事告诉雅典娜前辈也没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 因为就算是前辈也改不了规定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你打算把它就这么藏着养吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要这么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前 橙色行星的社长去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到小嘛就会想起它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位社长跟小嘛很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一点也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀… 前辈洗得舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说应该已经暴露了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢？爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的猜拳游戏…当然输的都是左手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在黑漆漆的地方会不会寂寞呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛在哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能…败露了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈的歌唱得真是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 左手可能没你想的那么笨拙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈今天公司休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在衣橱里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去上学了 前辈请慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这能持续到什么时候呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}这就是移居的一大原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}好 正如上次课堂上所说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}大规模的AQUA移居计划其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}已经是五十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}在那之前积累了无数次的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为昨天那件事 可能已经有人发现小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手可能没你想的那么笨拙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手总是在背后默默地支持着…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是今天起跟您同室的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝·卡罗尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛…小嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:16:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛它…小嘛它…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了呢？小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是被雅典娜前辈发现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后告诉公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…不能把事情往坏的地方想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到猫了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到爱丽丝的房间传来猫的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打开了衣橱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后它就逃跑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…不是雅典娜前辈丢掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈早就察觉到小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是为了掩饰小嘛的哭声才特意唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…比左手还要没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连小嘛都保护不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你回来 小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛也显得很安心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小嘛而言 爱丽丝也是重要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道您刚才唱歌是为了找小嘛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也是为了掩饰小嘛的哭声吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都没察觉到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚住进宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为害怕 睡不着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时你也是这样唱着歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是…还有 在我失眠的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也总是像这样 是为我而唱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为歌声…是要传达给别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟公司商量过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到了吗？虽然太小不易察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这孩子确实拥有蓝色的眼睛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子将成为橙色行星的新社长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色眼睛的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手…是超级伟大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在开始要练习向左手道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 我把烤奶油马铃薯忘在厨房里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么时候被爸爸吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下了一张字条…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写着「味道还可以 我期待你下次的作品」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便吃人家的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟说「还可以」 这算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很过分对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也因此从低落中走了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心变得很温暖 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 可能我们大家不知何时起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在被别人默默支持着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人无法察觉地 默默地…悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐上晃前辈的凤尾舟？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.72,0:24:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这么高兴也只有现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份 美好的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.71,0:24:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:22.10,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:31.27,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:40.88,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:51.64,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:59.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:10.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:19.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顏が すぐ こぼれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:29.32,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 伝えよう このときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:39.92,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風にのって あなたのもとへ 行くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:44.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:22.10,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}轻拂面颊的 温柔的风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:31.27,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌声中摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:40.88,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:51.64,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}闭上双眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:59.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}是风的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:10.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}来 让我们出发 向着闪亮的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:19.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}脸上的笑容 从未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:29.32,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}快 传达到彼方 把这份感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:39.92,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}托付给清风 带到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:44.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}水之精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:49.49,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水辺に映る いつもの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:57.06,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}穏やかに 流れる時間と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:00.75,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}移りゆく 季節の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:08.76,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}見つけたの 変わらぬ想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:13.07,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}聴いて 幸せの歌は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:19.69,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そう いつでも 心の中あふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:28.26,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.54,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:39.45,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:45.24,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:53.66,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:24:00.29,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:49.49,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不变的景色 倒映在水边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:57.06,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在缓缓流逝的时光和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:00.75,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不断变化的季节中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:08.76,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}寻觅到 那不变的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:13.07,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}听 那幸福的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:19.69,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}像这样 一直 满溢于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:28.26,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}所有的梦想 都将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.54,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 总会越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:39.45,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨后的彩虹 清澄的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:45.24,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鸟 总会展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:53.66,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}收集起胸中的爱意 定会见到彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:24:00.29,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心中常怀爱意 定能越过彩虹


